     </li> <li> The courses are taught by eminent faculty from Great Lakes and senior executives from leading analytics companies.
 </li><li>
The Program provides the candidates with hands on exposure to tools such as SAS, Tableau and actual industry case studies through virtual labs, assignments and project</li><li>
