<h4>Who is it for?</h4>
<p style="float: left;padding-right:15px;padding-left:15px;padding-bottom:10px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">

The PGP-BA Program is designed for working professionals who wish to embark on managerial careers in the analytics sector. The prior experience of a candidate need not be in analytics, though an analytic bent of mind would be preferable. A successful graduate degree, a minimum experience of two years and a keen interest in analytical problem solving are the only pre-requisites for applying to the Program. 
</p>
<h4>Career paths after PGPBA</h4>
<p style="float: left;padding: 0px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
The Post Graduate Program in Business Analytics (PGP-BA) equips you with the relevant knowledge and skills to pursue managerial careers with best of analytics companies or move the analytics roles within your existing organisation.
Though the roles would vary across organizations and would also depend on a candidate's experience levels, some of the indicative roles would be: Business Analyst / Senior Business Analyst, Manager (Analytics), Head (Analytics), Vice President (Analytics), Consultant, etc.
